TAKE: Pick up an item

Syntax: take <item>
        take <item> from <container>
        take all

DESCRIPTION:
  Picks up an item from the floor or from a container and places it in
  your inventory. The command get is an alias and works the same way.

EXAMPLES:
  take e-clip
  take sword from chest
  take admin handbook from chest
  take all

SEE ALSO: drop, give, inventory, get
